      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics including normalized RMS error and confidence intervals must be reported for hemolysis index predictions against experimental measurements.",
      "rationale": "Output comparison performed qualitatively for pressure-head curves. Hemolysis index was compared only at a single operating point without confidence intervals. Quantitative error metrics for all QOIs are absent."
