      "acceptanceCriteria": "The choice of turbulence model, hemolysis constitutive model, and non-Newtonian blood rheology model must each be justified with sensitivity analysis and literature benchmarks.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty is not assessed. The power-law hemolysis model is used without comparison to alternative formulations. Turbulence model selection is not justified for rotating machinery hemolysis at MRL 5."
